Salvador Videgain https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Salvador_Videgain 0 Salvador Videgain García (Madrid, February 26, 1886, – Madrid, October 12, 1947) was a famous actor of comedy and zarzuela during the first half of the 20th century in Spain and América. He was born and died in Madrid. He was known artistically as Salvador Videgain, was a theatrical entrepreneur, author, actor, theater director, Spanish.
